
Final Demo

1.	Choose any web site which requires authorization: login form should be present, google.com
2.	Implement 2 positive and 2 negative scenarios, at least one test scenario should have 7 steps: e.g.
    a.	Open page
    b.	Login as user
    c.	Open inbox folder
    d.	Search for some message
    e.	Open it
    f.	Verify that body and subject contains some text
    g.	Logout
3.	Run them from command line via Maven and show html report which was generated
Note: you should use PageObject pattern for your test framework. Any browser can be used (one of IE/FF/Chrome)




